{
  "stem": "23572.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I lived with a-- I had enough-- I think the Swiss Jewish community somehow arranged-- I lived with a Gentile family.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I now forgot their names.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I went to school, to a-- to a commercial school, in Zurich.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "When was this?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was 1940-- between '40-- around '44, '45.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "OK?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the rest-- the rest of the children set up another [? hashara ?] in [?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Aix-les-Bains, ?] which was the French part of Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They also, they were able to get out of the labor camps-- or the refugee-- I shouldn't call them labor camps.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were refugee camps, with no-- no hard labor.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I wish we had-- sometimes I wish we had something to do.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There was nothing for us to do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I learned how to smoke in those camps.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's about it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they-- they set up a [? harshara ?] in [?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Aix-les-Bains. ?] And eventually, when the war was over, all of [?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Aix-les-Bains ?] went to Palestine, OK?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Some of us remained in Switzerland after the war.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was one of them to remain in Switzerland because I was going to school and-- and everything else.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I got drunk.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And a whole bunch of us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's the only time I ever got drunk.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This was-- ?] We're not drinking, we-- we felt ourselves.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We touched ourselves, you know, am I still-- is it me?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I'm still alive?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The war is over, and I'm still alive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, Switzerland, we had newspaper, radio, and news, and everything else.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Was great jubilation that the war was-- the war was over.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was like, thank God.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, I mean-- Is it true?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Is-- What-- what happened?",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
